    <div class="rte" style="padding-bottom: 10px;margin-bottom: 20px;">
      Our 100% waterproof rainwear keeps you dry and keeps you comfortable so you can stay at it all day long. We offer rain jackets and rain suits for every application from all-purpose wear, to higher level protection from industrial, flame resistant, high visibility and premium recreation options.
    </div>
    <style>
      <!--
      @media(max-width: 740px) {
        h2 {
          border-bottom: 1px solid #f2f2f2;
        }
      }
    -->
    </style>
    <div class="product-row">
      <div class="product-index desktop-3 tablet-2 mobile-full">
        <a href="https://www.tingleyrubber.com/collections/all-purpose-rainwear">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0085/7807/2634/files/storm-champ-2-piece_400x400_crop_top.png?v=1619037647" alt="">
